<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/jpg" href="../img/lo.jpg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/admin.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxst.icons8.com/vue-static/landings/line-awesome/line-awesome/1.3.0/css/line-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Menu editeur</title>
</head>

<body>
    <style>
        @charset "utf-8";
        /* CSS Document */
        
        body {
            background: url(../img/back.png);
            margin: 0px;
            padding: 0px;
            background-color: white;
            font-family: calibri;
        }
        
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .services {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-evenly;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .s-heading {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .s-heading h1 {
            color: #576975;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin: 0px;
        }
        
        .s-heading p {
            color: rgba(87, 105, 117, 0.60);
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .s-box-container {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .s-box {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 300px;
            padding: 20px 25px;
            height: 300px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .s-box img {
            height: 75px;
        }
        
        .s-box h1 {
            color: #576975;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .s-box p {
            color: rgba(87, 105, 117, 0.90);
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .s-btn {
            width: 140px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.50);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: #576975;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .bar {
            width: 100px;
            height: 6px;
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            top: 0%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background-color: #D62839;
            border-radius: 0px 0px 10px 10px;
            display: none;
            animation: bar 0.5s;
        }
        
        .s-box:hover {
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            transition: all ease 0.3s;
        }
        
        .s-btn:hover {
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            border: 1px solid #4a90e2;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            transition: all ease 0.3s;
        }
        
        .s-box:hover .bar {
            display: block;
        }
        
        .menu-bar2 img {
            width: 45px;
            height: 30px;
            float: left;
            margin-top: 15px;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .menu-bar2 {
            height: 70px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .menu-bar2 ul {
            float: right;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        .menu-bar2 ul li {
            display: inline-block;
            line-height: 70px;
            margin: 0 5px;
        }
        
        .menu-bar2 ul li form button {
            text-decoration: none;
            background: transparent;
            color: white;
            border: transparent;
            padding: 1px 1px;
        }
        
        .menu-bar2 ul li form button:hover {
            color: #D62839;
            text-align: center;
            transition: .5s;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        
        .menu-bar2 ul li a {
            color: white;
            font-size: 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 7px 13px;
            border-radius: 1px;
        }
        
        .menu-bar2 ul li a:hover {
            background: #D62839;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: .5s;
        }
        
        @keyframes bar {
            0% {
                width: 0px;
            }
            100% {
                width: 100px;
            }
        }
        
        @media(max-width:1050px) {
            .s-box-container {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }
            .services {
                height: auto;
            }
            .s-heading {
                margin: 15px;
            }
            .s-box {
                flex-grow: 1;
            }
        }
    </style>


    <header>
        <div class="menu-bar2" id="click">
            <img src="../img/logo.png" alt="logo">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="http://127.0.0.1:3000/profil">   Accueil</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">  A propos</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">  Mon profil</a></li>
                <li>
                    <form action="/logout?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
                        <button type="submit">Deconnexion</button>
                    </form>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </header>

    <body>
        <br>
        <section class=" services ">
            <div class="s-heading ">
                <h1>M
                    <font color="#4BA3C3 ">en</font>u</h1>
                <p>Veuillez choisir l'une des options suivantes</p>
            </div>
            <div class="s-box-container ">

                <div class="s-box ">
                    <div class="bar "></div>
                    <img alt="1 " src="../img/blackverify.png " />
                    <h1>Verifier</h1>

                    <p>Verifier l'etat des dossiers des demmandeurs.</p>

                    <a class="s-btn " href="http://127.0.0.1:3000/verifier ">ICI</a>
                </div>

                <div class="s-box ">

                    <div class="bar "></div>

                    <img alt="2 " src="../img/blackcv.png " />

                    <h1>Saisir</h1>

                    <p>Saisie les informations des demandeurs.</p>

                    <a class="s-btn " href="http://127.0.0.1:3000/saisie ">ICI</a>
                </div>


            </div>


    </body>

</html>